Uses of Package
fr.gouv.vitam.tools.mailextract.core

  • Packages that use fr.gouv.vitam.tools.mailextract.core 
    Package Description
    fr.gouv.vitam.tools.mailextract.core
    Provides all core classes and method to do extraction and listing of mail boxes.
    fr.gouv.vitam.tools.mailextract.javamail
    Provides all classes to use JavaMail library.
    fr.gouv.vitam.tools.mailextract.libpst
    Provides all classes to use libpst library.
  • Classes in fr.gouv.vitam.tools.mailextract.core used by fr.gouv.vitam.tools.mailextract.core 
    Class and Description
    ArchiveUnit
    Class for SEDA Archive Unit managing metadata, objects, if any, and on disk representation.
    DateRange
    Class for automatic computation of start and end date of folders.
    ExtractionException
    Class for all exceptions thrown by the mailextract classes These exceptions are always fatal for the extraction or listing process.
    MailBoxFolder
    Abstract class for a mail box folder.
    MailBoxMessage.Attachment
    Utility class to encapsulate an attachment file with content and metadata (for now only filename) size and filename.
    MetaData
    Abstract class for all kinds of MetaData objects, in tree structure (array of objects, list of (key,object), string value} This very simple class is aimed to construct and write metadata structure.
    StoreExtractor
    Abstract factory class for operation context on a defined mailbox.
